La guerra terminó ...
... y ganó Linux
O eso es lo que dicen en:

<blockquote>
<a href="http://blogs.zdnet.com/open-source/?p=837" rel="bookmark" title="Permalink"> The war is over and Linux won</a> by <a href="http://zdnet.com">ZDNet</a>'s Dana Blankenhorn -- The truth of the assertion is in a chart near the back of the report. It shows that 83% of companies expect to support new workloads on Linux next year, against 23% for Windows. The move is slower for larger enterprises, but the direction is clear.
</blockquote>


